        "content": "<p>For a more general solution, you can do this:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">example</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ℕ</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">→</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ℤ</span><span class=\"o\">}</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">l</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ℕ</span><span class=\"o\">}</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"bp\">∑</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">&lt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">2</span><span class=\"bp\">*</span><span class=\"n\">l</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">∑</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">&lt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">l</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"mi\">2</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">*</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"mi\">2</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">*</span><span class=\"w\"> </s